<img src="graphics/news.jpg" align=right hspace=15>
<font size=-1>
This list contains major communications by Eli Lilly and Company to
the general public during the last six months.  It may not contain all
information released by the company during that period.  Company press
releases about our products may be found at the appropriate
<a href="../../products/index.html">product information</a>
section on this web site.  Earnings releases for the current calendar
year can be found in the <a href="../financial/index.html">financial
information</a> section of this web site.  Company press releases issued
prior to the six month period are not kept on this web site but can be
accessed through
<a href="/cgi-bin/exit-lilly.cmd?http://www.businesswire.com/cgi-bin/c_strip.sh+/cnn/lly.htm">Business Wire</a>.
<p>
<b>The information contained in these press releases was current on the date
the releases were issued.  Such information may become outdated over time.
By placing these releases on this web site, Lilly does not assume any
responsibility for updating any information in the releases.  Journalists 
who have additional questions are invited to contact their local Lilly
affiliate.</b>
</font>
